#: includes/Settings.php:223
msgid ""
"When checked, bulk export prepares all selected posts locally and writes "
"them to GitHub in one commit and one push, instead of one commit per post. "
"Much faster and far less likely to hit GitHub rate limits. Uncheck to go "
"back to a separate commit per post, e.g. to keep one commit per post in your "
"repository history."
msgstr ""

